707799f-a.title: Manhattan: 2nd Ave. - 21st St. E.
707799f-a.text:
Second Avenue, west side, from East 21st to 22nd
Street's, showing the R. C. Church of the Epip-
hany in the center of this frontage. At the left
is the apartment house, No. 245 East 21st Street,
V6G ~ 53E3
